    Let mutable m be a new Seq of Word32.
    Push word32(1633837952) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(0) to m.
    Push word32(24) to m.
    Let kk be sha256K().
    Let result be sha256Compress(state, m, kk).
    Repeat for w in result:
        Show intOfWord32(w).
